| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5333 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cc00c223-81c8-5c1c-9d40-d6b9b20ee44d"
